seealso `[SkinDriver]`

This is a C++ interface to `[skin_driver_attr]`.

FUNCTION SkinDriverAttr: (patchCount: SkinPatchSize, moduleCount: SkinModuleSize, sensorCount: SkinSensorSize)
	Constructor

	Set the driver attributes.

	INPUT patchCount
		The number of patches in this piece of skin.  See `[skin_driver_attr::patch_count](skin_driver_attr#patch_count)`
	INPUT moduleCount
		The number of modules in this piece of skin.  See `[skin_driver_attr::module_count](skin_driver_attr#module_count)`
	INPUT sensorCount
		The number of sensors in this piece of skin.  See `[skin_driver_attr::sensor_count](skin_driver_attr#sensor_count)`

FUNCTION getPatchCount: (): SkinPatchSize
	Get the number of patches

	This function returns the number of patches.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_driver_attr::patch_count](skin_driver_attr#patch_count)` attribute.

FUNCTION getModuleCount: (): SkinModuleSize
	Get the number of modulees

	This function returns the number of modules.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_driver_attr::module_count](skin_driver_attr#module_count)` attribute.

FUNCTION getSensorCount: (): SkinSensorSize
	Get the number of sensores

	This function returns the number of sensors.

	OUTPUT
		Returns the `[skin_driver_attr::sensor_count](skin_driver_attr#sensor_count)` attribute.
